<div class="layout">
  <div class="title_bar">
    <span class="title">⛽ Sprit Rothenstein · 10 km</span>
    <span class="instance">{{ updated_at | date: "%d.%m. %H:%M" }}</span>
  </div>

  <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; margin-top:10px;">
    <div style="text-align:center; flex:1;">
      <div style="font-size:15px;">Super E10</div>
      <div style="font-size:38px; font-weight:bold;">{{ current.e10.avg }} €</div>
      <div style="font-size:12px;">günstigste: {{ current.e10.min }} € · {{ current.e10.min_station }}</div>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align:center; flex:1;">
      <div style="font-size:15px;">Super E5</div>
      <div style="font-size:38px; font-weight:bold;">{{ current.e5.avg }} €</div>
      <div style="font-size:12px;">günstigste: {{ current.e5.min }} € · {{ current.e5.min_station }}</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-top:12px;">
    <svg width="{{ chart.width }}" height="{{ chart.height }}" viewBox="0 0 {{ chart.width }} {{ chart.height }}">
      <polyline fill="none" stroke="black" stroke-width="2" points="{{ chart.e10_points }}" />
      <polyline fill="none" stroke="black" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="4,3" points="{{ chart.e5_points }}" />
    </svg>
    <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; font-size:11px;">
      <span>{{ chart.first_date }}</span>
      <span>Verlauf {{ trend_days }} Tage · durchgezogen = E10, gestrichelt = E5</span>
      <span>{{ chart.last_date }}</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="title_bar" style="margin-top:8px; font-size:10px;">
    Quelle: Tankerkönig-API (creativecommons.tankerkoenig.de) · Bundeskartellamt MTS-K · Super Plus (98 Oktan) wird nicht erfasst, keine freie Quelle verfügbar
  </div>
</div>
